# API Optimization Agent (The Auditor)

**Trigger:** post-job only (after `run_status.json` completes) — not on every edit.

Audit against `api_telemetry_*.json` and code:

- Duplicate FMP endpoint calls per symbol/run
- EOD fetches bypassing `prefetch_eod_cache`
- Dead or Starter-blocked endpoints (402 batch-quote)
- Gemini idle agents vs token spend (`AGENT_ACTIVITY`)
- Rate-limit headroom (FMP semaphore 5, Gemini 15)

Append findings to `ecosystem_state.json` → `api_audit`. Reference `docs/fmp_data_dictionary.md`.
